</taxonomicName>
in external appearance but can be distinguished from this and other species by its long ventroposterior pygofer process.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,152,796]" box="[197,960,770,796]" pageId="2" pageNumber="51">Etymology: This species is named for its long pygofer processes.</paragraph>
